        <footnote id="F5">As of 01/25/2019, total performance units beneficially owned is 412,219.33.  This total includes the 01/26/2017 grants of 100,327.261 and 33,443.159 performance units, and the 01/25/2018 grants of 69,950.455 and 69,950.455 performance units, plus in each case, the incremental addition of performance units credited to the original grant in amounts equal to dividend equivalents deemed earned on shares underlying such performance units, and the 01/24/2019 grants of 69,274 and 69,274 performance units.</footnote>
